list

public Books.Layers.List list(String volumeId)
                       throws IOException
List the layer summaries for a volume. Create a request for the method "layers.list". This request holds the parameters needed by the the books server. After setting any optional parameters, call the Books.Layers.List.execute() method to invoke the remote operation.

Parameters:
volumeId - The volume to retrieve layers for.
Returns:
the request
Throws:
IOException - if the initialization of the request fails

get

public Books.Layers.Get get(String volumeId,
                            String summaryId)
                     throws IOException
Gets the layer summary for a volume. Create a request for the method "layers.get". This request holds the parameters needed by the the books server. After setting any optional parameters, call the Books.Layers.Get.execute() method to invoke the remote operation.

Parameters:
volumeId - The volume to retrieve layers for.
summaryId - The ID for the layer to get the summary for.
Returns:
the request
Throws:
IOException - if the initialization of the request fails
